{"tid":1450960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:14:23.000Z","uid":231758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"60f2f1a92e849e3625aba645d63ca1ad45bd3fd1","tid":1450960,"uid":231758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:08:20.000Z","msg":"標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=3d7bb7b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=e6405afc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"f77865c8dc141e43295468af3d777a01f5b8402f","tid":1450960,"uid":11698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家 準備長期作戰<br />\n聽日唔好再玩接機 笑笑口和理非<br />\n記住個女仔半邊面係血既樣<br />\n記住班黑警1m距離內開槍+掉人落電梯<br />\n記住依家有幾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日12/8 Full gear塞爆+癱瘓 成個機場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔唱歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔接機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔衝禁區<br />\n<br />\n保持憤怒 統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i